(vii)  in  liaison  with  the  executing  agency,  coordinate  the  preparation  and 
implementation of specific case studies on the lessons learnt from the super 
ministry  reform  or  intersector  administration  system that  has  been piloted  in 
some cities; 
(viii)  coordinate provincial (and local) case studies and review existing policies related 
to environmental administration within the scope of this project;  
(ix)  review  financing  mechanisms  for  environmental  administration  and  the 
environmental fiscal policy system;  
(x)  participate and present topics in project seminars and workshops;  
(xi)  compile  and  finalize  the  TA  final  report  and  coordinate  inputs  from  the 
